Allow me to state an alternate point of view...<br>
<br>
For some, EQ Romance &gt; RL Romance.  RL Romance takes work.  RL romance takes money.  RL Romance has consequences.<br>
<br>
EQ Romance...maybe you'd spend some plat, but cash is in infinite supply, unlike what you make in Real Life.<br>
<br>
EQ Romance...you don't have to meet the parents, the siblings, the aunts and uncles.  Just the friends, maybe a concerned guild leader.<br>
<br>
EQ Romance...if things get too heavy, too dramatic, too upsetting, you can turn it off.  It isn't as easy to do in Real Life.<br>
<br>
